data.description: This adorable ranch home offers a half-acre, corner lot and a quiet neighborhood! 2, - 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, partial basemen. 2 living spaces plus a dining room are just a few of the things you will love about this home. The white kitchen cabinets, granite, and stainless-steel appliances will make you want to be in your kitchen. The current setup could easily be converted to a 3 bedroom with the addition of doors. The 2-car garage, 2 covered porches, fenced in yard, gorgeous spring bloom Magnolias and 2 sheds are all the exterior bonuses. 2015 updates include hvac, range, refrigerator and dishwasher.
